welcome_message_body: Welcome to Port Orange, where the charm of a small town meets the beauty of the Atlantic coast. Known for its picturesque parks and stunning beaches, we invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at New Smyrna Beach Municipal Airport serves commercial and private flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Daytona Beach International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Daytona Beach International Airport serves domestic flights operated by various airlines.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Daytona Beach International Airport serves international flights operated by select airlines.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport is used for charter and seasonal flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights at Bunnell Flagler County Airport.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is reserved for private and charter flights only.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
